......tailwind shortcut.......
kuno custom property/value jodi tailwind e use korte hoi tkn jevabe likte hobe:

<h2 class="text-[#FABE4C]">Be the Penguins</h2>
evabei muloto kuno custom property tailwind e likte hoi,ortat likboto html tag e class er vitore kintu  likar syntex hocce etai jmn:

class="text-[#FABE4C]">
class="bg-[#FABE4C]">
class="border-[#FABE4C]">

evabe kuno tag er class er vitore tailwind er class name(bg/border) then hypen diye 3rd bracket er vitore oi custom property/value/colorname ta.